  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "See, this is a good example of why I want to kill you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "You're ignorant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 263.0,
    "text": "Heed my words, Finn, as the miller's wheel forever outrages the seed, so the good apple boringly receives his neighbor's worm."
